spec_data.Name: perl-MLDBM
spec_data.Description:
This module can serve as a transparent interface to any TIEHASH package
that is required to store arbitrary perl data, including nested references.
Thus, this module can be used for storing references and other arbitrary
data within DBM databases.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 12:59:29 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Store multi-level hash structure in single level tied hash
